#: cards:1
msgid ""
"<p>This is for recording the current status of an Activity Resource Record.&nbsp; There are three levels:</p>\n"
"\n"
"<ul>\n"
"\t<li><strong>Backlog-Skeleton.</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;Only basic information about the activity has been created, and no associated heritage Records, if applicable, have been created.</li>\n"
"\t<li><strong>Backlog - Full/Published.</strong>&nbsp; All Mandatory and Required data fields have been added, but no associated heritage Records, if applicable, have been created or linked.</li>\n"
"\t<li><strong>Active- Full/Published.&nbsp;</strong>All Mandatory and Required data fields have been added, and all&nbsp;associated heritage Records, if applicable, have been created and linked.&nbsp;</li>\n"
"</ul>\n"
msgstr ""
"<p>Hei hopu tēnei i te tūnga o nāianei o tētahi Pūkete Rauemi Hohenga.&nbsp; E toru ōna taumata:</p> \n"
"<ul> \n"
"<li><strong>Rangitakimuri- Tōkau.</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;Kua hangaia he mōhiotanga taketake anake mō tēnei mahi, ā, kāore anō he Pūkete taonga tuku iho pāhono kia hangaia, mehemea e whai pānga ana ēnei.</li> \n"
"<li><strong>Rangitakimuri - Katoa/Kua whakaputaina.</strong>&nbsp; Kua oti katoa ngā āpure raraunga Whakahau, E Tika ana te tāpiri, engari kāore anō he Pūkete taonga tuku iho pāhono kia hangaia, kia honoa rānei, mehemea e whai pānga ana ēnei.</li> \n"
"<li><strong>Hohe- Katoa/Kua whakaputaina &nbsp;</strong>Kua oti katoa ngā āpure raraunga Whakahau, E Tika ana te tāpiri, ā, &nbsp kua hangaia, kua honoa hoki ngā Pūkete taonga tuku iho pāhono katoa, mehemea e whai pānga ana.&nbsp;</li> \n"
"</ul>"

