#: cards:1
msgid ""
"<p><strong>Full Address</strong></p>\n"
"\n"
"<p>Where it is convenient, this can be used to record the full address. This can be used to aid migration from legacy systems with less sophisticated recording practice</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><strong>Address Parts</strong></p>\n"
"\n"
"<p>To better represent the complexity of addresses each constituent part has been modelled.</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><strong>Building Name</strong></p>\n"
"\n"
"<p>Use to record the actual name of a building where known.</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><strong>Building Number</strong></p>\n"
"\n"
"<p>Use to record the number(s) assigned to a building. This may be a single number (eg. 45) or a range separated by a &#39;-&#39;&nbsp;(eg. 13-21).</p>\n"
"\n"
"<p><strong>Building Number Sub-Street</strong></p>\n"
"\n"
"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"<p><strong> Kāinga Noho</strong></p> \n"
"<p>Ina ngāwari te mahi, ka taea tēnei te whakamahi hei hopu i te wāhi noho katoa. Ka taea tēnei te whakamahi hei āwhina i te whitinga mai i ngā pūnaha tawhito he iti iho ngā hōhonutanga mō te hopu kōrero</p> \n"
"<p><strong> Ngā Wāhanga Kāinga Noho</strong></p> \n"
"<p>Kia pai ake ai te whakaahua i te hōhonu o ngā wāhinoho, kua āta whakatauiratia ia wāhanga.</p> \n"
"<p><strong>Ingoa Whare</strong></p> \n"
"<p>Whakamahia hei hopu i te ingoa ake o tētahi whare ina mōhiotia.</p> \n"
"<p><strong>Tau Whare</strong></p> \n"
"<p>Whakamahia hei hopu i te (ngā) tau i tautapatia ki tētahi whare. He nama takitahi pea tēnei (hei tauira 45) he awhe rānei, e noho ana he &#39;-&#39;&nbsp;(hei tauira. 13-21).</p> \n"
"<p><strong>Tiriti-roto Tau Whare</strong></p> \n"
"<p>&nbsp;</p>"

